  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>1. Perform retail sales duties in promoting home and electrical appliances in our retail store.</p>\n<p>2. Possess good salesmanship, good attitude, positive mindset and a good team player.</p>\n<p>3. IT Savvy and customer oriented with keen interest in handling customers.</p>\n<p>4. Perform area cleaning duties and maintain good housekeeping practices in the store.</p>\n<p>5. Any other duties as assigned by the superior.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<p>1. Ability to service customers in a friendly and approachable manner.</p>\n<p>2. Possess some computer knowledge to input customer data into our system.</p>\n<p>3. Willing to work on a 6-day work week – Retail hours 12.30pm – 9pm and off on a fixed weekday.</p>\n<p>4. Those with some retail background will have an added advantage.</p>\n<p>5. Able to start work immediately or within short notice.</p>\n<p>6. Those without experience but with keen interest in handling customer and IT Savvy are welcome to apply.</p>\n<p>7. Candidate must possess at Primary / Secondary education or O level / Diploma in Retail Sales or its equivalent.</p>",
